title: God's Wisdom | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: God's Wisdom | Victoria Osteen
description:
The Bible says if we need wisdom, we only need to ask God for it. When you seek wisdom, God will do incredible things in your life!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
